        {
            "title": "七國集團財長將於周二召開會議 討論稀土和烏克蘭問題",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"七國集團財長將於周二召開會議 討論稀土和烏克蘭問題\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"648\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t6mCciRBFexX_WgSwNZVFQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0OA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/023022d0-d3f6-11f0-bf73-d69c27f557bd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">七國集團財長將於周二召開會議 討論稀土和烏克蘭問題</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%83%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E8%B2%A1%E9%95%B7%E5%B0%87%E6%96%BC%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%AC%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0-%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E7%A8%80%E5%9C%9F%E5%92%8C%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-093329487.html",
