            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "高盛貴金屬交易主管Binet-Laisne據悉將離職",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士透露，高盛集團貴金屬交易主管Benjamin Binet-Laisne將離開該行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著對沖基金和貿易公司搶奪人才，Binet-Laisne的離職凸顯了銀行在留住貴金屬市場交易員方面所面臨的挑戰。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：黃金火爆行情帶熱招聘市場 對沖基金、貿易商開出高薪爭奪交易人才(1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛在該市場中的規模居前，近期從StoneX Group Inc.招募了Pranav Bhatia，擔任其貴金屬交易部門的交易員。根據Binet-Laisne的領英資料，他在高盛任職約十年，在這一市場頗具資歷。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fbab3485-a8d5-3a1a-ba65-2d38776ce9b1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛拒絕就他的離職置評。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貴金屬價格的瘋漲加劇了人才爭奪戰。最近數月，倫敦市場平均每周交易的現貨黃金規模超過5000億美元，自2021年以來成長了約兩倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Goldman’s Top Precious Metals Trader Binet-Laisne Leaves Bank</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E8%B2%B4%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1binet-laisne%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E5%B0%87%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7-133716954.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 22:54:32",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日本選戰將拉開大幕 高市早苗支持率略有下滑",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"高市早苗攝影師：Kiyoshi Ota/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eIUPMx12UopLIMEaMA48lA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8ed52a24a7eb50117dae4050917d4cc7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:高市;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/高市\">高市</a>早苗攝影師：Kiyoshi Ota/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 周末進行的幾項民意調查顯示，日本首相高市早苗的支持率略有下降，表明她在2月初提前選舉的決定存在風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">民調初步展現了選民對高市早苗上周宣布提前大選的看法。儘管按歷史標準來看，她的支持率仍然相當高，但出現一定下滑表明部分選民並不認同她提前大選的決定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">共同社的民調顯示，高市早苗的支持率下滑4個百分點至63%；讀賣新聞的民調顯示，她的支持率下滑4個百分點至69%；ANN的民調顯示，其支持率下滑5.4個百分點至57.6%。日經新聞和每日新聞民調顯示的高市早苗支持率降幅更大，前者下降8個百分點至67%，後者下降10個百分點至57%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f5da65fc-2239-3b63-8e5d-ebbafd3c3af7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在周一下午舉行的黨首辯論中，高市早苗對支持率下滑不以為然。相反，她態度強硬地賭上自己的首相之位。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果自民黨和維新會不能贏得多數席位，我將立即辭職，」她說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《每日新聞》的報導顯示，41%的受訪者不認同高市早苗解散國會的時機，因為那恰逢國會例會開幕日，將不可避免地導致始於4月新財年的預算推遲通過。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過儘管有所下滑，但高市早苗的支持率在一些民調中仍保持在60%以上，表明她仍然擁有相當高的人氣，也讓她有一定的回旋餘地。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：日本首相高市早苗確認將於2月8日舉行提前選舉</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原最大在野黨立憲民主黨和自民黨的前執政聯盟夥伴公明黨合併組建的新政黨「中道改革聯合」，儘管努力挑戰執政黨，但似乎進展艱難。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ANN的民調顯示，26%的受訪者對中道改革聯合抱有希望，而62%的人表示不抱希望。讀賣新聞的調查也呈現出類似趨勢，22%的受訪者表示抱有希望，69%則表示對其不抱希望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">正式競選活動將於周二開始，選民將於2月8日前往投票站投票。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Takaichi’s Ratings Dip as Japan Heads Into Election Campaign</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0%E5%B0%87%E6%8B%89%E9%96%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%95-%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A9%E8%8B%97%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%8E%87%E7%95%A5%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91-080445031.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 21:04:30",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "擋下一位潛在競爭者 英國首相斯塔默恐難高枕無憂 其他對手或伺機而動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 英國首相基爾·斯塔默的競爭對手們尋找借口發起領導權挑戰。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:斯塔默;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/斯塔默\">斯塔默</a>周末阻撓了一位潛在挑戰者，但此舉反而可能給了其他人出擊的理由。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周日，斯塔默的盟友阻止了大曼徹斯特市長Andy Burnham作為工黨候選人參加即將舉行的戈頓和丹頓補選，使他無法明確進入議會。沒有議席，他就無法挑戰首相職位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯塔默周一表示，此舉是為了優先考慮對工黨至關重要的五月地方選舉，並避免在曼徹斯特進行耗資巨大的新市長競選活動。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dc790d48-1af8-3bb9-b6ba-3c7ed3bf7d64-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據英國新聞協會報導，斯塔默周一表示，「我們必須將全部精力集中在這些[地方]選舉上。無論是資金還是人力，資源都應集中用於必須進行的選舉，而不是那些我們不必舉行的選舉。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士透露，斯塔默本人周日上午在工黨全國執行委員會（NEC）小組會議上表示，Burnham參選將引發長達數月的「心理劇」。由於討論未公開，知情人士要求匿名。他還指出，Burnham曾承諾將完成大曼徹斯特市長任期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，僅工黨副領袖Lucy Powell為Burnham發聲，向委員會小組表示他在補選中最有希望擊敗奈傑爾·法拉奇領導的英國改革黨。該委員會小組充斥著對首相效忠的成員，最終以8比1的投票結果阻止Burnham參選。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上周債券投資者對一位更左翼傾向、主張自由支出型領導人的擔憂引發市場動盪，英國國債在早盤交易中走高。30年期國債殖利率（該品種對財政風險的敏感度高於短期債券）周一早間下跌4個基點至5.21%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這或許能讓斯塔默稍感寬慰，但恐怕難以阻止黨內左翼對手策劃下一步行動，也難阻右翼競爭者伺機而動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Starmer Stops Burnham But Rivals Say It Only Delays His Fate (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Lucy White、Joe Mayes、Alice Gledhill.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%93%8B%E4%B8%8B-%E4%BD%8D%E6%BD%9B%E5%9C%A8%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E6%96%AF%E5%A1%94%E9%BB%98%E6%81%90%E9%9B%A3%E9%AB%98%E6%9E%95%E7%84%A1%E6%86%82-%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%88%96%E4%BC%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%80%8C%E5%8B%95-112118617.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 20:13:57",
